 Adekunle Kosoko, better known as Adekunle Gold has taken to his Instagram page to gush over his wife Simi. Today, Sunday, March 14, loads of countries around the world have taken this special day to honour mothers. Reacting to the mother’s day celebration, Adekunle shared lovely photos of his wife Simi and his child. He shared photos and videos of when Simi was carrying their baby Deja and when she welcomed her baby. Nigerian singer noted that he and his daughter Adejare are the luckiest to have Simi. Sharing the adorable photos and videos, he captioned; Happy 1st Mother’s Day to you my baby. Deja and I are the luckiest to have you, Magic ?